features: 【Retro Style Dining Table】: This wood rectangular dining table uses solid wood as the main material and using antique finish, this dining table set presents a kind of reverence for the original, natural and mottled beauty. Whether enjoying an everyday meal with the fam or hosting a dinner party, this table is a must-have for your abode.

【MDF & Solid Wood】: Our dining table tops are made of MDF and solid wood veneer with a clear wood texture and smooth touch. All other parts are made of solid wood for excellent stability, durability and heirloom quality.

【Exquisite Craftsmanship】: The 4" thickness columnar rubber wood table legs and the curved iron frame add retro and industrial atmosphere to your room. Rubber feet on the bottom of the legs help protect the floor from scratches. The smooth, waterproof table top can easily be cleaned with a simple wipe down, for hassle-free maintenance.

【Ideal for Family Use】: 78"x40" spacious countertop is convenient enough for your family dinners and party. Table load-bearing 300LBS. Ideal for dinette, kitchen, and dining areas, this dining table seats up to 8 people, perfect for families to enjoy meal times together.

【Full/Partial assembly required】: This dining table comes with detailed instructions, and it can be installed step by step following the instructions, which can help you complete the assembly as soon as possible.
